{"tid":1546990,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"國師又中！陳雲：Be water ！ (2014年11月27日)","createTime":"2019-09-06T13:43:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T05:27:16.000Z","uid":118346,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"348267d26ef7f4e0ddba742c551d039cf1cf43c9","tid":1546990,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T13:43:16.000Z","msg":"陳雲：旺角陣地不見，留駐的人變成流動的人。流動的人是潮水，每晚旺角來一次漲潮，累積幾日，潮水越來越大，終於淹沒和衝崩特務兵團的海堤。《道德經》曰：「上善若水。」李小龍說的Be water。<br />\n我覺得港共想滅亡，否則豈會如此愚昧？留着彌敦道陣地在耗日子，豈不是很好嗎？"},{"pid":"c4e75a75846646d9ce4c8ff8da81f66397f3c924","tid":1546990,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T13:44:02.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1545337/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1545337/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9018d17f7129eed0f7a8246d880686f5c0d462b6","tid":1546990,"uid":290761,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T13:53:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A8vAmVU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA8vAmVU.jpg&h=305434b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屯門區校友街坊們過黎幫手啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"392bfb54099c6417678a3146ed5ab018c75c2b1b","tid":1546990,"uid":224479,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T15:29:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.g